iv class=\"absolute\" style=\"z-index:10;opacity:0;transform:translateY(80px)\"><div class=\"relative w-[8.5rem] xs:w-40 sm:w-56 max-w-full select-none overflow-hidden rounded-2xl bg-white p-1.5 sm:p-2 shadow-2xl ring-2 ring-slate-300\"><div class=\"relative flex h-24 xs:h-28 sm:h-36 items-center justify-center overflow-hidden rounded-xl bg-gradient-to-br from-sky-400 to-blue-600\"><div class=\"absolute inset-0 opacity-30 [background-image:radial-gradient(circle_at_20%_20%,white,transparent_40%)]\"></div><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1.5\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-layers h-10 w-10 xs:h-12 xs:w-12 sm:h-16 sm:w-16 text-white drop-shadow-lg\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M12.83 2.18a2 2 0 0 0-1.66 0L2.6 6.08a1 1 0 0 0 0 1.83l8.58 3.91a2 2 0 0 0 1.66 0l8.58-3.9a1 1 0 0 0 0-1.83z\"></path><path d=\"M2 12a1 1 0 0 0 .58.91l8.6 3.91a2 2 0 0 0 1.65 0l8.58-3.9A1 1 0 0 0 22 12\"></path><path d=\"M2 17a1 1 0 0 0 .58.91l8.6 3.91a2 2 0 0 0 1.65 0l8.58-3.9A1 1 0 0 0 22 17\"></path></svg><span class=\"absolute left-1.5 top-1.5 sm:left-2 sm:top-2 flex h-6 w-6 sm:h-8 sm:w-8 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-white/90 text-xs sm:text-sm font-bold text-slate-800 shadow\">1</span><span class=\"absolute right-1.5 top-1.5 sm:right-2 sm:top-2 rounded-full px-1.5 py-0.5 sm:px-2 text-[8px] sm:text-[10px] font-bold uppercase tracking-wide bg-slate-100 text-slate-600\">Común</span></div><div class=\"px-1 pb-1 pt-1.5 sm:px-1.5 sm:pb-1.5 sm:pt-2 text-left\"><h3 class=\"text-xs sm:text-sm font-bold leading-tight text-slate-800 line-clamp-1\">Canal de Capa 2 (Rollup)</h3><p class=\"text-[9px] sm:text-[11px] font-medium uppercase tracking-wide text-primary\">Concepto</p><p class=\"mt-1 sm:mt-1.5 line-clamp-2 text-[10px] sm:text-[11px] leading-snug text-slate-500\">Procesa acciones fuera de la red principal. Reduce a cero el costo de energía (Gas) de tus cartas por 2 turnos.</p><div class=\"mt-1.5 sm:mt-2 flex items-center justify-between border-t border-slate-100 pt-1.5 sm:pt-2 text-[11px] sm:text-xs font-semibold\"><span class=\"flex items-center gap-0.5 sm:gap-1 text-rose-500\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-swords h-3 w-3 sm:h-3.5 sm:w-3.5\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><polyline points=\"14.5 17.5 3 6 3 3 6 3 17.5 14.5\"></polyline><line x1=\"13\" x2=\"19\" y1=\"19\" y2=\"13\"></line><line x1=\"16\" x2=\"20\" y1=\"16\" y2=\"20\"></line><line x1=\"19\" x2=\"21\" y1=\"21\" y2=\"19\"></line><polyline points=\"14.5 6.5 18 3 21 3 21 6 17.5 9.5\"></polyline><line x1=\"5\" x2=\"9\" y1=\"14\" y2=\"18\"></line><line x1=\"7\" x2=\"4\" y1=\"17\" y2=\"20\"></line><line x1=\"3\" x2=\"5\" y1=\"19\" y2=\"21\"></line></svg> <!-- -->20</span><span class=\"flex items-center gap-0.5 sm:gap-1 text-sky-500\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-shield h-3 w-3 sm:h-3.5 sm:w-3.5\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M20 13c0 5-3.5 7.5-7.66 8.95a1 1 0 0 1-.67-.01C7.5 20.5 4 18 4 13V6a1 1 0 0 1 1-1c2 0 4.5-1.2 6.24-2.72a1.17 1.17 0 0 1 1.52 0C14.51 3.81 17 5 19 5a1 1 0 0 1 1 1z\"></path></svg> <!-- -->20</span><span class=\"flex items-center gap-0.5 sm:gap-1 text-amber-500\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-zap h-3 w-3 sm:h-3.5 sm:w-3.5\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M4 14a1 1 0 0 1-.78-1.63l9.9-10.2a.5.5 0 0 1 .86.46l-1.92 6.02A1 1 0 0 0 13 10h7a1 1 0 0 1 .78 1.63l-9.9 10.2a.5.5 0 0 1-.86-.46l1.92-6.02A1 1 0 0 0 11 14z\"></path></svg> <!-- -->1</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></section><section class=\"relative mx-auto max-w-6xl px-6 pb-20\"><div class=\"grid gap-5 md:grid-cols-3\"><div class=\"rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 bg-white/70 p-6 shadow-sm backdrop-blur transition hover:-translate-y-1 hover:shadow-lg text-left\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(30px)\"><span class=\"flex h-11 w-11 items-center justify-center rounded-xl bg-indigo-50 text-indigo-600\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-book-open h-6 w-6\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M12 7v14\"></path><path d=\"M3 18a1 1 0 0 1-1-1V4a1 1 0 0 1 1-1h5a4 4 0 0 1 4 4 4 4 0 0 1 4-4h5a1 1 0 0 1 1 1v13a1 1 0 0 1-1 1h-6a3 3 0 0 0-3 3 3 3 0 0 0-3-3z\"></path></svg></span><h3 class=\"mt-4 text-lg font-bold text-slate-800\">Fase 1 · Fundamentos</h3><p class=\"mt-1.5 text-sm text-slate-500\">Bloques, transacciones y wallets en combates equilibrados para no frustrarte.</p></div><div class=\"rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 bg-white/70 p-6 shadow-sm backdrop-blur transition hover:-translate-y-1 hover:shadow-lg text-left\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(30px)\"><span class=\"flex h-11 w-11 items-center justify-center rounded-xl bg-indigo-50 text-indigo-600\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-shield-check h-6 w-6\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M20 13c0 5-3.5 7.5-7.66 8.95a1 1 0 0 1-.67-.01C7.5 20.5 4 18 4 13V6a1 1 0 0 1 1-1c2 0 4.5-1.2 6.24-2.72a1.17 1.17 0 0 1 1.52 0C14.51 3.81 17 5 19 5a1 1 0 0 1 1 1z\"></path><path d=\"m9 12 2 2 4-4\"></path></svg></span><h3 class=\"mt-4 text-lg font-bold text-slate-800\">Fase 2 · Seguridad</h3><p class=\"mt-1.5 text-sm text-slate-500\">Scams, phishing y hackeos. Aprende a usar &#x27;counters&#x27; contra amenazas reales.</p></div><div class=\"rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 bg-white/70 p-6 shadow-sm backdrop-blur transition hover:-translate-y-1 hover:shadow-lg text-left\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(30px)\"><span class=\"flex h-11 w-11 items-center justify-center rounded-xl bg-indigo-50 text-indigo-600\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-trophy h-6 w-6\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M10 14.66v1.626a2 2 0 0 1-.976 1.696A5 5 0 0 0 7 21.978\"></path><path d=\"M14 14.66v1.626a2 2 0 0 0 .976 1.696A5 5 0 0 1 17 21.978\"></path><path d=\"M18 9h1.5a1 1 0 0 0 0-5H18\"></path><path d=\"M4 22h16\"></path><path d=\"M6 9a6 6 0 0 0 12 0V3a1 1 0 0 0-1-1H7a1 1 0 0 0-1 1z\"></path><path d=\"M6 9H4.5a1 1 0 0 1 0-5H6\"></path></svg></span><h3 class=\"mt-4 text-lg font-bold text-slate-800\">Fase 3 · Web3</h3><p class=\"mt-1.5 text-sm text-slate-500\">Smart Contracts, DeFi y gobernanza. Derrota al jefe final del ecosistema.</p></div></div></section></div></div><!--$--><!--/$--></main></div></div><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/webpack-95bc6416891d3552.js\" id=\"_R_\" async=\"\"></script><script>(self.__next_f=self.__next_f||[]).push([0])</script><script>self.__next_f.push([1,\"1:\\\"$Sreact.fragment\\\"\\n2:I[59175,[\\\"5775\\\",\\\"static/chunks/a1a9fd37-9715490483aa4f9c.js\\\",\\\"6990\\\",\\\"static/chunks/6990-c00cd5258a18a344.js\\\",\\\"5096\\\",\\\"static/chunks/5096-3d213677ea3efb1d.js\\\",\\\"8512\\\",\\\"static/chunks/8512-47735c96a55e1c0d.js\\\",\\\"8963\\\",\\\"static/chunks/8963-7d204123021a9b77.js\\\",\\\"2039\\\",\\\"static/chunks/2039-98e9d64ffda21619.js\\\",\\\"812\\\",\\\"static/chunks/812-e8f8c1848c313c4e.js\\